# execute SQL inside migrations

You can execute direct SQL in migrations with *execute* method

~~~ruby
Class DoSomethingMigration < ActiveRecord::Migration
  def up 
    execute "Update categories set ......"
  end
#...
~~~



date: 2012-08-00






