# Rails pluck


Fetch only one column SQL query 

    Option.select("DISTINCT type").pluck(:type)
    #  =>   SELECT type FROM `options


Fetch only one column with unique values SQL query 

    Option.select("DISTINCT type").pluck(:type)
    # =>   SELECT DISTINCT type, type FROM `options`





