# HashWithIndifferentAccess

in Rails 

~~~ruby
h = Hash.new
h['aaa'] = 'hello'

p h['aaa']
# hello

p h[:aaa]
#nil



hwia = HashWithIndifferentAccess.new
hwia['aaa'] = 'hello'

p hwia['aaa']
# hello

p hwia[:aaa]
# hello
~~~

*params* in rails controllers are also  indifferent access hash 




