# print random number in formated string

### with with 4 char format

like:

    "90  "
    "590 "

do 

~~~ruby
col = rand(9999)
print printf( "%-4s",col)
~~~

much cooler approach 


~~~ruby
"%4s" % rand(9999)
"%-4s" % rand(9999)
~~~


### with leading zeros 4 char format

~~~ruby
"%04d" % rand(9999)
~~~

    "0010"
    "0300"


date 2011-00-00

