# remove nonasci characters from string 

If you wan't to remove nonasci characters from string like 

    s = "Grüße"

solution:

    s.gsub!(/\P{ASCII}/, '')

or 

    s.delete!("^\u{0000}-\u{007F}")
    #=> Gre




